#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.67"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.67:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.67:0.2"
msgid "7. Devatāvagga"
msgstr "7. A God"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.67:0.3"
msgid "67. Mittasutta"
msgstr "67. Friends"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: pāpamitte → pāpake mitte (mr)
msgctxt "an6.67:1.1"
msgid ""
"“‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu pāpamitto pāpasahāyo pāpasampavaṅko, pāpamitte "
"sevamāno bhajamāno payirupāsamāno, tesañca diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjamāno "
"ābhisamācārikaṃ dhammaṃ paripūressatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, it’s totally impossible that a mendicant with bad friends, "
"companions, and associates, while frequenting, accompanying, and attending, "
"and following their example, will fulfill the practice dealing with the "
"supplementary regulations."

msgctxt "an6.67:1.2"
msgid ""
"‘Ābhisamācārikaṃ dhammaṃ aparipūretvā sekhaṃ dhammaṃ paripūressatī’ti netaṃ "
"ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without fulfilling the practice dealing with supplementary regulations, it’s "
"impossible to fulfill the practice of a trainee."

msgctxt "an6.67:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘Sekhaṃ dhammaṃ aparipūretvā sīlāni paripūressatī’ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without fulfilling the practice of a trainee, it’s impossible to fulfill "
"ethics."

msgctxt "an6.67:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘Sīlāni aparipūretvā kāmarāgaṃ vā rūparāgaṃ vā arūparāgaṃ vā pajahissatī’ti "
"netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Without fulfilling ethics, it’s impossible give up desire to be reborn in "
"the realm of luminous form or in the formless realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.67:2.1"
msgid ""
"‘So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko, "
"kalyāṇamitte sevamāno bhajamāno payirupāsamāno, tesañca diṭṭhānugatiṃ "
"āpajjamāno ābhisamācārikaṃ dhammaṃ paripūressatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"It’s possible that a mendicant with good friends, companions, and "
"associates, while frequenting, accompanying, and attending, and following "
"their example, will fulfill the practice dealing with the supplementary "
"regulations."

msgctxt "an6.67:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘Ābhisamācārikaṃ dhammaṃ paripūretvā sekhaṃ dhammaṃ paripūressatī’ti "
"ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Having fulfilled the practice dealing with supplementary regulations, it’s "
"possible to fulfill the practice of a trainee."

msgctxt "an6.67:2.3"
msgid "‘Sekhaṃ dhammaṃ paripūretvā sīlāni paripūressatī’ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
msgstr ""
"Having fulfilled the practice of a trainee, it’s possible to fulfill ethics."

msgctxt "an6.67:2.4"
msgid ""
"‘Sīlāni paripūretvā kāmarāgaṃ vā rūparāgaṃ vā arūparāgaṃ vā pajahissatī’ti "
"ṭhānametaṃ vijjatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"Having fulfilled ethics, it’s possible give up desire to be reborn in the "
"realm of luminous form or in the formless realm.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.67:2.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
